text: Night of the Living Deb, is a 2015 American zombie apocalyptic comedy film. It was directed by Michael Cassidy, Kyle Rankin, Chad Nicholson and co-Director Kyle Rankin starring Maria Thayer, Michael Cassidy, Ray Wise, Chris Marquette, Syd Wilderand David Krumholtz. ==References== Category:2015 comedy movies Category:Zombie movies Category:2015 horror movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American horror thriller movies Category:2010s English- language movies Category:Apocalyptic movies Category:Movies set in Maine
